---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Waterfall Technologies LTD: Establishing U.S. Presence Seamlessly — Case Study | Nelexa"
  description="How Nelexa enabled Waterfall Technologies LTD to establish their U.S. presence with seamless hardware procurement, assembly, and installation services."
>
  <article class="bg-black">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-36 pb-14 bg-black overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[900px] h-[400px] bg-primary-800/25 rounded-full blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-30"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 border border-primary-500/30 text-primary-300 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Hardware Procurement</span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 border border-primary-500/30 text-primary-300 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Assembly &amp; Testing</span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 border border-primary-500/30 text-primary-300 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Delivery &amp; Installation</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white mb-6">
            Waterfall Technologies LTD: <span class="gradient-text italic">Establishing U.S. Presence Seamlessly</span>
          </h1>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/50">
            <span class="font-semibold text-white">Waterfall Technologies LTD</span> · January 20, 2024 · 4 min read
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Body -->
    <section class="relative py-14 bg-black">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-lg prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-headings:text-white prose-p:text-white/70 prose-li:text-white/70 prose-strong:text-white prose-a:text-primary-400 hover:prose-a:text-primary-300">
          <h2>Background</h2>
          <p>Waterfall Technologies LTD is a UK-based company that wanted to establish its own infrastructure presence in the United States, specifically in New York. The goal was to deploy and manage equipment within a facility they fully owned and controlled, ensuring long-term stability and independence in the U.S. market.</p>
          <p>They didn't want to deal with multiple vendors or complicated logistics. They wanted one team that could handle everything from start to finish — and that's where Nelexa came in.</p>

          <h2>What We Did</h2>
          <p>From the beginning, our focus was on making the process as seamless as possible for Waterfall's leadership team in the UK. We took ownership of the entire project:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Hardware procurement</strong> — We sourced and ordered the hardware directly to our facility.</li>
            <li><strong>Assembly and preparation</strong> — Once it arrived, our team assembled and tested all components to meet Waterfall's exact build requirements.</li>
            <li><strong>Delivery and installation</strong> — After completing final checks, we coordinated secure transport and installation at their New York location, ensuring the systems were online and fully functional.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Throughout the process, Waterfall's team stayed informed and updated without needing to travel or coordinate with multiple vendors.</p>

          <h2>The Outcome</h2>
          <p>Waterfall's New York deployment was completed smoothly and on schedule. Their team was able to bring the new systems online without managing international logistics or hiring local contractors.</p>
          <p>By handling everything from procurement through installation, Nelexa helped Waterfall establish a fully independent presence in New York, giving them greater regional access and operational flexibility without overextending their UK resources.</p>

          <h2>Final Thought</h2>
          <p>Establishing a physical presence in another country requires precision and trust. For Waterfall Technologies, partnering with Nelexa meant having a reliable team to handle the technical details and ensure everything was deployed correctly the first time.</p>
          <p>Nelexa continues to support businesses like Waterfall in achieving operational independence, whether through colocation, logistics coordination, or full-scale infrastructure deployment.</p>
          <p><em>Need help establishing your infrastructure presence in new markets? <a href="/contact">Contact Nelexa</a> for comprehensive hardware procurement, assembly, and installation services.</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-black border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="relative glass-card overflow-hidden p-10 md:p-14 text-center">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600/15 to-accent-700/10"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white mb-4">Ready to achieve similar results?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Let our enterprise infrastructure experts help you implement similar solutions for your organization. Contact us to discuss your specific requirements.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
              <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-xl shadow-primary-900/40">Get Custom Solution</a>
              <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">View More Case Studies</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
